your fingers, not kiss them.

01:42.722 --> 01:44.958
Somebody hid my work box
behind a fucking Zamboni.

01:44.960 --> 01:47.664
I mean, it's almost like
he's openly craving love.

01:47.666 --> 01:49.166
But not contemporary love.

01:49.168 --> 01:50.670
It's like he channeled Freddie Mercury

01:50.672 --> 01:52.807
and borrowed a stage move from 1982.

01:52.809 --> 01:54.978
- You know what I think?
- [Milo] Forget the fingertips.

01:54.980 --> 01:58.017
There's some serious
shit going on, all right?

01:58.019 --> 02:00.088
