02:08.841 --> 02:10.810
It's a chunky brown crayon.

02:10.812 --> 02:12.814
The point is, Phil was our leader,

02:12.816 --> 02:13.882
and without a true leader...

02:13.884 --> 02:15.185
What about Bill?

02:15.187 --> 02:17.055
...we go to lawlessness,

02:17.057 --> 02:19.159
disorder, chaos!

02:19.161 --> 02:21.565
Exhibit A was our cases missing, all right?

02:21.567 --> 02:23.635
I mean, do you think The
Head and The Heart would dare

02:23.637 --> 02:25.906
to fuck with us if Phil was still around?

02:25.908 --> 02:27.543
You actually think

02:27.545 --> 02:29.481
The Head and The Heart hid our cases?

02:29.483 --> 02:30.983
Yes! Without Phil, a true leader,

02:30.985 --> 02:33.989
the fucking opening act
feels emb... emboldened

02:33.991 --> 02:35.425
to just take out their
petty aggressions on us.

02:35.427 --> 02:36.828
Fuck yeah!

02:36.830 --> 02:38.866
Mark my words, this
woeful lack of leadership

02:38.868 --> 02:40.368
will destroy this band.

02:40.370 --> 02:43.709
It's just the fingertips of the iceberg.

02:43.711 --> 02:45.378
- [chuckles]
- What about Bill?

02:45.380 --> 02:47.182
Bill's already cracking
from the pressure, all right?

02:47.184 --> 02:48.619
It's too much for him.

02:48.621 --> 02:49.687
Someone say there were wings?

02:49.689 --> 02:51.593
Fuck yeah! Back here!

02:53.898 --> 02:56.300
