08:32.508 --> 08:34.677
to my, um, room...

08:34.679 --> 08:36.078
- Hmm.
- ...and it never arrived.

08:36.081 --> 08:37.448
- It's a brown...
- Brown.

08:37.450 --> 08:40.889
