09:32.327 --> 09:34.563
No, it's this thing
Christopher started doing,

09:34.565 --> 09:36.166
kissing his fingertips.

09:36.168 --> 09:38.805
Oh, yeah, that... right.
That's... that's new.

09:38.807 --> 09:42.445
