disconcerting and disturbing.

09:42.447 --> 09:44.483
<i>Someone needs to tell him
to stop, and since Phil's</i>

09:44.485 --> 09:47.021
<i>not there, that
someone is you, Bill.</i>

09:47.023 --> 09:48.190
<i>♪ 'Cause I can't
have you anymore ♪</i>

09:48.192 --> 09:49.860
I just fucking miss Phil.

09:49.862 --> 09:52.264
