09:52.266 --> 09:54.503
Like the ancient Aztecs
didn't look into someone's soul

09:54.505 --> 09:56.974
and feel a fucking eternity
in the flash of a second?

09:56.976 --> 09:58.310
Come on!

09:58.312 --> 10:00.280
