<i>♪ Hardcore ♪</i>

36:07.213 --> 36:12.221
<i>♪ I don't want to
do it anymore ♪</i>

36:12.223 --> 36:14.192
And then we'll cut... he cut in like...

36:14.194 --> 36:16.831
<i>♪♪♪</i>

36:16.833 --> 36:18.433
Ahh!

36:18.435 --> 36:22.543
<i>♪♪♪</i>

36:22.545 --> 36:25.549
[Christopher plays soft music]

36:25.551 --> 36:30.561
<i>♪♪♪</i>

36:34.434 --> 36:37.438
[band playing blues rock music]

36:37.440 --> 36:39.810
<i>♪ Your brother said he locked
you up in the bedroom ♪</i>

36:39.812 --> 36:41.146
Ha!

36:41.148 --> 36:44.252
<i>♪♪♪</i>

36:44.254 --> 36:48.093
<i>♪ Your sister said she
throw away the key ♪</i>

36:48.095 --> 36:50.498
<i>♪♪♪</i>

36:50.500 --> 36:52.301
<i>♪ Well there's
nothing in the world ♪</i>

36:52.303 --> 36:55.341
<i>♪ Nothing in the world
that's gonna stop you ♪</i>

36:55.343 --> 36:57.913
<i>♪♪♪</i>

36:57.915 --> 37:01.119
<i>♪ Hell no not even me ♪</i>

37:01.121 --> 37:06.064
<i>♪♪♪</i>

37:11.643 --> 37:14.212
<i>♪ Every time I get
to feel like this ♪</i>

37:14.214 --> 37:18.053
<i>♪♪♪</i>

